text: Pälkäne is a municipality in Pirkanmaa, Finland. As of 31 December 2021, the municipality had a population of 6,439. Nearby municipalities are Hattula, Hämeenlinna, Kangasala, Padasjoki and Valkeakoski. The former municipality of Luopioinen was merged on 1 January 2007. == Other websites == * Municipality of Pälkäne – Official website Category:Municipalities of Pirkanmaa
